OL,3,CRory McIlroy criticises Ryder Cup
OL,4,Ccrowds 'unacceptable and abusive
OL,5,Cbehaviour'
OL,7,FRory McIlroy said police dogs should
OL,8,Fhave been let off their leashes after
OL,9,Fhis wife was struck by a beer can
OL,10,Fthrown from the crowd at the Ryder Cup
OL,11,Ftournament.
OL,13,FThe Northern Irishman was heckled
OL,14,Fthroughout the three-day tournament as
OL,15,FAmerican spectators shouted crude
OL,16,Fpersonal taunts and attempted to
OL,17,Fdistract him as he prepared to play
OL,18,Fshots.
