OL,7,FEurope emerged victorious from the
OL,8,Ftournament in Long Island, New York,
OL,9,Fseeing off a roaring comeback attempt
OL,10,Ffrom the US.
OL,12,FOn Saturday, a dozen state troopers
OL,13,Fwere brought in to manage the
OL,14,Fchanting, heckling and boisterous
OL,15,Fcrowd in check, while a marshal warned
OL,16,Fspectators to "keep it clean."
