OL,4,Ccrowds 'unacceptable and abusive
OL,5,Cbehaviour'
OL,7,F"I wish they had let the dogs off the
OL,8,Fleashes," said McIlroy in a press
OL,9,Fconference after Europe held off a
OL,10,Fremarkable United States fightback to
OL,11,Fwin the trophy 15-13 on Sunday.
OL,13,FHe continued: "Look, nothing was going
OL,14,Fto happen ` there wasn't going to be a
OL,15,Fphysical altercation or anything like
OL,16,Fthat ` but there was a lot of language
OL,17,Fthat was unacceptable and abusive
OL,18,Fbehaviour.
