OL,3,CRory McIlroy criticises Ryder Cup
OL,4,Ccrowds 'unacceptable and abusive
OL,5,Cbehaviour'
OL,7,F"It's a minority of the crowd, it's
OL,8,Fnot the majority. The majority of
OL,9,Fpeople here are true golf fans and are
OL,10,Frespectful, but I don't think we
OL,11,Fshould ever accept that in golf."
OL,13,FIn footage of the incident shared on
OL,14,Fsocial media, Erica looked shocked
OL,15,Fafter being hit by the projectile, but
OL,16,Fwas not hurt.
