OL,7,FShane Lowry, McIlroy's playing partner
OL,8,Fat the time, said: "I was out there
OL,9,Ffor two days with Erica and the amount
OL,10,Fof abuse that she received was
OL,11,Fastonishing."
OL,13,FMcIlroy rose above the taunts to
OL,14,Fdeliver three-and-a-half points across
OL,15,Fthe foursomes and fourballs sessions
OL,16,Fbut was unable to maintain his
OL,17,Fmomentum as he was beaten by Scottie
OL,18,FScheffler on the 18th hole in the
OL,19,Fsingles.
