OL,7,F"I felt like I was running on empty,"
OL,8,Fhe said.
OL,10,FUltimately, it did not matter as
OL,11,FEurope denied the US an unlikely
OL,12,Fcomeback victory.
OL,14,FDespite being seven points behind as
OL,15,FSunday's singles session, the US
OL,16,Froared back into contention with a
OL,17,Fseries of wins, but Europe did just
OL,18,Fenough to win.
