OL,7,FAfter securing the cup, the European
OL,8,Fteam shared a video taunting the US
OL,9,Fpresident, who is a big golf fan,
OL,10,Fchanting: "Are you watching, Donald
OL,11,FTrump?"
OL,13,FTrump responded: "Yes, I'm watching.
OL,14,FCongratulations!"
OL,16,FReflecting on the team's performance,
OL,17,FMcIlroy said: "We did what we needed
OL,18,Fto do and we are going to celebrate
OL,19,Flike there is no tomorrow."
